        <hr class="bold-divider" />

        <section id="benefits">
            <h2>il tuo vantaggio</h2>
            <p>Building a website can feel overwhelming. I simplify the process and deliver tangible benefits:</p>
             <div class="benefits-grid">
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <h3>üöÄ Blazing Fast Sites</h3>
                    <p>Using Astro means top-tier performance baked in, leading to better user experience and SEO rankings.</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="benefit-item">
                    <h3>üí∞ Affordable Solutions</h3>
                    <p>My streamlined process focuses on your essential needs, providing professional quality without enterprise agency costs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
