        <hr class="bold-divider" />

        <section id="process">
             <h2>My Process: Simple & Transparent</h2>
             <p>I follow a clear roadmap to ensure your project stays on track and meets your goals.</p>
             <img src="/placeholder-roadmap-detailed.svg" alt="Workflow: Discovery, Wireframing, Design, Development, Testing, Launch, Support" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-block: 1.5rem; border: 1px dashed #ccc; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
