                <li><strong>Discovery:</strong> We discuss your goals, audience, and requirements.</li>
                <li><strong>Wireframing/Planning:</strong> We outline the structure and user flow.</li>
                <li><strong>Design:</strong> Creating the visual look and feel based on your brand.</li>
